     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"Pensions from the TfL Pension Fund increased in April 2017.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "This is based on the rise in the Retail Price Index over the 12 months to September 2016.",
